Package: varmonitor
Type: Package
Title: Risk management tools: Value-at-Risk monitor
Version: 0.1.8
Date: 2021-05-08
Author: Gatti Riccardo, Lin Francesco
Maintainer: Lin Francesco <fkl@francescolin.com>
Description: The package provides tools to estimate the Value-at-Risk and Expected Shortfall according to the parametric and analitical approach under the following assumptions: no time-varying volatility or changes market variables are following a normal distribution.
License: GPL-3
